    public class AttributesListPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    A reusable panel that accepts the model name and allows adding, removing, and changing of database attributes.

    • Constructor Detail

      • AttributesListPanel

        public AttributesListPanel(NamedObj model)
        Construct a AttributesListPanel. Add swing Components to the panel. Add a listener for the "Add Attribute" button, which adds a ModelAttributePanel to the tabbed pane and delete buttons that are mapped to each ModelAttributePanel.
        Parameters:
        model - The model that is being saved to the database.
